OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 12 MAY
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1937FThe BBC produces its first
OL,7,Foutside broadcast - coverage of the
OL,8,Fcoronation of King George VI and Queen
OL,9,FElizabeth.
OL,10,
OL,11,FThis is the first use of the BBC's TV
OL,12,Foutside broadcast van.
OL,13,
OL,14,FNine thousand TV sets are sold in the
OL,15,FLondon area ahead of the broadcast.
OL,16,
OL,17,FA small portion of this broadcast is
OL,18,Fone of the earliest surviving examples
OL,19,Fof British television - filmed
OL,20,Foff-screen at home by an engineer with
OL,21,Fan 8mm cine camera.
OL,22,
